OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly rain in the east quickly
OL,6,Fclearing to leave a day of sunshine
OL,7,Fand frequent showers. Showers will be
OL,8,Fheavy at times, with hail and thunder
OL,9,Fpossible. Remaining rather breezy.
OL,10,FTemperatures around average for the
OL,11,Ftime of year.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FShowers continuing through
OL,14,Fthe evening, but gradually easing
OL,15,Fovernight, although some persisting in
OL,16,Fthe west. Staying breezy, rather
OL,17,Fcloudy and mild across all areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
