OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FLargely cloudy at first on
OL,6,FWednesday, but some brighter spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping at times into the
OL,8,Fafternoon. A few spots of rain
OL,9,Fpossible where the cloud thickens,
OL,10,Fmainly over western hills.
